Package: harpSat
Title: Read And Manipulate Satellite Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Andrew", "Singleton", , "andrewts@met.no", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Package for reading satellite data with harp. Includes
    functions to read from various satellite data files and to resample
    swath data to a regular grid.
